{
  "texts": [
    "It enables applications that connect a language model to sources of context.",
    "This integrates various components such as embedding, vector databases, LLMs, etc.",
    "Using these components, we can provide external documents to the significant language models and build AI applications such as chatbots seamlessly.",
    "Faiss-cpu, Facebook AI Similarity Search, is a Python library, used for efficient similarity search, embeddings of multimedia documents that are similar to each other, and clustering of dense vectors.",
    "The sentence-transformers package enables the utilization of pre-trained models for sentence embeddings in Python projects."
  ]
}